Example with Vectors

Target Word:

fox

Embedding:

fox = [0.45, 0.71, 0.28]

The network predicts probabilities for all words.

| Word  | Probability |
| ----- | ----------: |
| quick |        0.91 |
| brown |        0.87 |
| jumps |        0.84 |
| over  |        0.79 |
| dog   |        0.05 |


The model learns that quick, brown, jumps, and over are the surrounding words.

